name: Prayatna - An Attempt for Holistic Development and Social Advancement Samiti
briefDescription: Prayatna - An Attempt for Holistic Development and Social Advancement Samiti is Located in Indore, Madhya Pradesh. Organisation working on the issue of women & child development, women empowerment, street children, health, education and rural/urban poors. Organisation intervention area is Indore and Ujjain district of Madhya Pradesh.
